0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":642,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/21\/trust-heaven-quran-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37999,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Faith: The trust descended from heaven to people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The covenant of faithfulness descended from the heavens and settled in the hearts of men. The Quran was revealed and they read it in the Quran and learned it from the Sunnah.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6848, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/salat-al-witr-ahl-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":37999,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Witr prayer recommended, not obligation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is numerically odd and He loves what is odd, so perform the Witr prayer, O people of the Quran!\u201d Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe Witr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abu